<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27Aug1915"><font color="red">27 August 1915</font>, <cite>Pound/Joyce</cite> (Ezra Pound to JJ): I put your name down in a prominent place among the probable contributors. Do send whatever you have, to me direct, and then if the scheme falls through I can pass &apos;em on to Pinker.</div>
